  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "Ruger 57 5.7x28毫米手枪",
      "en": "Ruger 57 5.7x28 pistol"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "Ruger 57",
      "en": "Ruger 57"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "鲁格-5.7是一款由斯特姆-鲁格公司于2019年12月推出的半自动手枪。这是自2012年Excel Arms MP-57问世以来，首款采用传统构型并采用5.7×28毫米弹药的半自动手枪。其安全措施包括：1911式双侧手动保险、内置扳机保险、轻量化击针、采用中性平衡设计、具有充分咬合度与强劲弹簧张力的阻铁，以及击锤卡榫装置，确保除非扣动扳机时击锤不会接触击针。",
      "en": "The Ruger-5.7 is a semi-automatic pistol introduced in December 2019 by Sturm, Ruger & Co. It is the first traditionally-styled semi-automatic pistol to be chambered for the 5.7×28mm cartridge since the introduction of the Excel Arms MP-57 in 2012. Safety features include: 1911-style ambidextrous manual safety; an integrated trigger safety; light-weight firing pin; neutrally balanced sear with significant engagement and strong spring tension; and hammer catch to help prevent the hammer from contacting the firing pin unless the trigger is pulled."
    },
